wdi-IQ.SPI.PIL1.def: The data use overall score is a composite score covering five dimensions: (i) the legislature, (ii) the executive branch, (iii) civil society (including sub-national actors), (iv) academia and (v) international bodies.  Scores range from 0-100 with 100 representing the best score.
wdi-IQ.SPI.PIL1.name: Statistical performance indicators
wdi-IQ.SPI.PIL1.source: Statistical Performance Indicators, The World Bank (https://datacatalog.worldbank.org/dataset/statistical-performance-indicators)
